comment:
* Class containing the source identifiers used to update device management-related system
         * drawable.

variables.name: NOTIFICATION
variables.comment: * A source identifier indicating that the updatable drawable is used in notifications.

variables.name: PROFILE_SWITCH_ANIMATION
variables.comment:
* A source identifier indicating that the updatable drawable is used in a cross
             * profile switching animation.

variables.name: HOME_WIDGET
variables.comment:
* A source identifier indicating that the updatable drawable is used in a work
             * profile home screen widget.

variables.name: LAUNCHER_OFF_BUTTON
variables.comment:
* A source identifier indicating that the updatable drawable is used in the launcher
             * turn off work button.

variables.name: QUICK_SETTINGS
variables.comment: * A source identifier indicating that the updatable drawable is used in quick settings.

variables.name: STATUS_BAR
variables.comment: * A source identifier indicating that the updatable drawable is used in the status bar.
